Dialogue.Value: [A light shines from just above,this massive floating stone.]
[It’s too bright to make out any,details.]
[Agh! You startled me!,....Whew. Let’s just skip the,whole “Boo，outsiders!” thing.]
[I come out here to just unwind,sometimes. I dunno.,It’s peaceful.]
[Nah，just this dumb rock.,Where else would count as,“heaven-like”，though....?]
[I’m sure we’ll figure it out.,I never really got “heaven” from,this place anyways.]
[Really? Heaven’s high up，this,is as high as you can go.,The logic checks out.]
[No，no，I meant the Undernet’s,kinda.... evil? You get what I,mean，right?]
[Not really....?,Some of these guys are pretty,fun，actually.]
[I don’t know what I expected....,....Hold on a second. Is it just,me，or did it get brighter?]
[Hold on，hold on....,I’ve still got spots in my eyes....]
[“Heaven-like”，remember.,Don’t get carried away.,Let’s see what the big deal is.]
